{"data":{"page":{"id":"ee48c92f-4d4e-5c9d-8021-370f90492de5","html":"<p class=\"align-center\">\n<a class=\"btn\" href=\"http://work.joanmira.com/webs/slater/\" target=\"_blank\">Launch archived template</a>\n<a class=\"btn\" href=\"http://work.joanmira.com/webs/slaterusa/\" target=\"_blank\">Launch archived USA template</a></p>\n<p>While I was working at Slater Labs as a software engineer, I took the creation of the company website as a side project. I wanted to explore new things, like the use of animated 3d models, playing with the webcam and the microphone and voice recognition. In a way, I wanted to mimic a little bit the kind of interactive behaviours that we were building for the desktop applications of the company.</p>\n<p>\n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 1000px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 57.099999999999994%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/9a288d2f9693b43681f81a47a6e112b4/877ff/1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/9a288d2f9693b43681f81a47a6e112b4/d2504/1.jpg 500w,\n/static/9a288d2f9693b43681f81a47a6e112b4/877ff/1.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  </p>\n<p>\n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 1000px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 75.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"2\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/c07f607f3299fc74eb69b81880715902/877ff/2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c07f607f3299fc74eb69b81880715902/d2504/2.jpg 500w,\n/static/c07f607f3299fc74eb69b81880715902/877ff/2.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  </p>\n<p>\n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 1000px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 101%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"3\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/ae3b51240c92f8b45c8c15ad0dc316a2/877ff/3.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ae3b51240c92f8b45c8c15ad0dc316a2/d2504/3.jpg 500w,\n/static/ae3b51240c92f8b45c8c15ad0dc316a2/877ff/3.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  </p>\n<p>There is also a template for Slater Labs USA, but this wasn’t completed, so it’s more like a quick mockup. The color of the sky changes based on the time.</p>","fields":{"prefix":"2004"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Slater Labs","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"resize":{"src":"/static/4ed5adcd60fcdf0bd21477076de66553/d927d/logo.jpg"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/slaterlabs/","source":"work"}}